kowhai moth
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a caterpillar <i>Uresiphita polygonalis maorialis</i> also known as <i>Mecyna maorialis</i> that strips leaves of broom, clover, kowhai and lupin.


Origin: Maori
